text.tspan: Deaths from pneumonia in elderly people by risk factor, World, 1990 to
Shown is the number of deaths of people 70 years and older from pneumonia and other lower respiratory diseases by
risk factor that was estimated to be responsible for these deaths.
Source: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
